<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 xiàng qián xiàng qián! xiàng qián! shǒu ná shèng líng de bǎo jiàn;
 dōng bàn qiú, xī bàn qiú, fèng zhǔ de míng zǒu shàng yī quān.
 kǔn bǎng le mó guǐ, chú miè le sā dàn,
 shén de róng yào chōng mǎn, quán shì jiè dōu gǎi biàn.</lyrics>
<title>xiàng qián xiàng qián 迦南560</title>
<hymn_number>560</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>